And so what kind of contributions are we looking for?

00:46:13.040 --> 00:46:24.439
So we're open to hearing your ideas and ask for design choices, project governance, hands on engineering, as well as how to maintain an activity use package.

00:46:24.439 --> 00:46:32.760
And if you want to reach out, please reach out to Mark Bailey and James Black, whose emails are listed here.

